    "notes": [
      {
        "text": "Unlike regular equipment, all Ultimate equipment uses Sunstone, Minerals and Scroll of XProtect in the upgrading process.",
        "text_cn": "与普通装备不同，所有终极装备在升级过程中都需要消耗太阳石、矿物和防爆卷轴。"
      },
      {
        "text": "Once a weapon is converted to Ultimate, it gains an additional two different random stats (both the stat and its amount).",
        "text_cn": "当武器转换为终极武器后，它会额外获得两个不同的随机属性（包括属性类型和数值）。"
      },
      {
        "text": "At levels 6 and 10, the weapon gains an additional orange random stats.",
        "text_cn": "在等级达到 +6 和 +10 时，武器会获得额外的橙色随机属性。"
      }
    ],
